track_notes:
Follow the forest road to the waterfall. Ascend the East side of the falls. Then follow the fence / wall to the ridge. At the ridge ascend to the summit platau. The waterfall and ascent to the ridge is tough the rest is easy.

To have a good day go to a HEMA Curleywee GM/HSS-131. I will put the full track on this site.

This was the full route including HEMA GM/HSS-131. It is worth adding on. From Curleywee there are two routes to the forest road. The one I took into the basin or along the ridge. I did wish I had left bottles of water at the waterfall where I left the forest road to go up Lamachan so I could pick them up on the return walk. Walk time inc Activations 7h30m walk time 4h15m.
track_title: Full walk to Lamachan and Curleywee
